All-in-One Order Tracking Solution
TrackingMore has been serving the eCommerce industry for over 10 years with the best order tracking solutions.
As a robust shipment tracking API aggregator connected to 1,300+ global carriers, TrackingMore allows online marketplaces to centralize their logistics, which benefits sellers and delights buyers, builds brand reputation, and makes the marketplace more attractive.
By using TrackingMore, e-commerce platforms can:
Give sellers more shipment visibility
Improve post-purchase experience for end customers
Reduce customer support & retention costs and increase logistics efficiency
Help resolve disputes between sellers and buyers by providing transparent and accurate shipment tracking information, builds trust and communication.
